<vsep class="fewlines"/>

<poem>
<l>Was it not Fate, that, on this July midnight</l>
<l>Was it not Fate (Whose name is also Sorrow)</l>
<l>That bade me pause before that garden gate</l>
<l>To breathe the incense of those slumbering roses ?</l>
<vsep class="dots"/>
<vsep class="dots"/>
<l>(Ah ! bear in mind this garden was enchanted !)</l>
</poem>

<p class='r3'>Edgar A<s>LLAN</s> P<s>OE</s>.</p>

